## Conclusion

The FPGA Smart Traffic Light Controller successfully demonstrates traffic sequencing, pedestrian crossing management, and emergency vehicle prioritization using a robust FSM architecture. The project highlights digital design, verification, and simulation skills applicable to FPGA and VLSI development.
